Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.select

Class SelectServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<SelectComponentType,Select>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.select.SelectServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SelectService, Insertion
public class SelectServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<SelectComponentType,Select> implements SelectService
Implementation of the SelectService interface, providing methods to select options, retrieve available and selected options, and determine if certain options are visible or enabled. Extends AbstractComponentService to handle the creation and retrieval of Select instances.

This class relies on the SelectComponentType to identify the correct component for select-type elements, allowing test automation to manage dropdowns, multi-select fields, or similar widgets in a consistent manner.
